sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Browser as Browser UI
    participant Api as Node.js API
    participant Edge as C++ Edge Core
    participant Field as BACnet/IP Device

    Browser->>Api: Request data or command
    Api-->>Browser: HTTP/JSON response
    Api-->>Browser: SSE telemetry/alarm update
    Api->>Edge: gRPC call
    Edge-->>Api: gRPC response
    Edge->>Field: BACnet/IP read/write
    Field-->>Edge: BACnet/IP response
